adjectives.description: irrelevant (comparative more irrelevant, superlative most irrelevant)

entries.meaning: Not at all related: totally unrelated, wholly unconnected, completely inapplicable.
examples: Coordinate terms: unrelated, unassociated, uncorrelated, random, stochastic, alien

entries.meaning: Not usefully related: not associated in any way that is important or useful to the context being discussed: not materially applicable; having connections not applicable in the present situation.
examples: Coordinate terms: unimportant, immaterial, incidental, inapplicable
